          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Design tokens, color mappings, and spacing tokens that define the Dropdown Menu's visual language.</p>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="variants" class="doc-section-title">Variants</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">6 variants across Type (3) &times; Size (1) &times; RTL (2).</p>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Axis</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><strong>Type</strong></td><td><code>Single Select</code>, <code>Multi Select</code>, <code>With Sections</code></td><td>Controls item type, header, and footer presence.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Size</strong></td><td><code>Small</code></td><td>Currently only Small is available (Medium planned).</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>RTL</strong></td><td><code>False</code>, <code>True</code></td><td>Mirrors the entire panel layout for RTL locales.</td></tr>
              </tbody>
