        <!-- ========== USAGE ========== -->
        <div class="tab-content" id="tab-usage" style="display:none;padding-top:32px;">
          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="when-to-use" class="doc-section-title">When and Where to Use</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Dropdown menus present contextual lists of actions or options attached to a trigger element.</p>
            <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:24px;margin-top:24px;">
              <div style="padding:24px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;">
                <h3 style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>When to use</h3>
                <ul class="doc-list" style="border:none;background:transparent;padding-left:20px;font-size:14.5px;">
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">Offer a contextual list of actions or options attached to a trigger element (button, icon button, field).</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">When there are too many options to display inline (typically 3 or more).</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">When the user needs to select one option and immediately apply it (Single Select).</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">When the user needs to select multiple options before committing (Multi Select).</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;">When options fall into distinct logical groups (With Sections).</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:24px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;">
                <h3 style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#e42527" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>When NOT to use</h3>
                <ul class="doc-list" style="border:none;background:transparent;padding-left:20px;font-size:14.5px;">
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">For navigation &#8212; use a Nav Menu or Sidebar instead.</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">When there are only 2 options &#8212; use a Toggle or two Buttons.</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">When options need descriptions or rich content &#8212; use a Popover or Dialog.</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;">As a form select input &#8212; use a Select Field component instead.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <hr class="doc-divider"/>
          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="alignment-placement" class="doc-section-title">Alignment &amp; Placement</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Consistent positioning ensures dropdown menus appear predictably relative to their triggers.</p>
            <ul class="doc-list">
              <li><strong>Below Trigger:</strong> The panel should appear directly below the trigger element, aligned to its left edge.</li>
              <li><strong>Left-Aligned:</strong> Default alignment is left-aligned with the trigger. In RTL mode, the panel aligns to the right.</li>
              <li><strong>Z-Index:</strong> Dropdown panels must appear above all page content. Use a z-index of at least 1000.</li>
              <li><strong>Viewport Boundary:</strong> If the panel would extend beyond the viewport, flip it above the trigger or shift it horizontally to remain visible.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <hr class="doc-divider"/>
          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="detailed-guidelines" class="doc-section-title">Complete Do's and Don'ts</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Guidelines for effective dropdown menu usage.</p>
            <div class="do-dont-grid">
              <div class="do-card"><span class="card-label">Do</span><ul>
                <li><strong>Keep labels short:</strong> 1&#8211;4 words per item for fast scanning.</li>
                <li><strong>Close Single Select immediately</strong> on item selection.</li>
                <li><strong>Use Show Header=OFF</strong> when the trigger label already provides context.</li>
                <li><strong>Provide a "Clear All" path</strong> in Multi Select (<code>Show Footer=ON</code>).</li>
                <li><strong>Use With Sections</strong> when 2+ logical groupings exist with 3+ items each.</li>
                <li><strong>Use Multi Select</strong> when the user needs to confirm before applying.</li>
              </ul></div>
              <div class="dont-card"><span class="card-label">Don't</span><ul>
                <li><strong>No sentence labels:</strong> Don't use sentence-long descriptions as item labels.</li>
                <li><strong>No single-pick multi:</strong> Don't use Multi Select for single-pick scenarios.</li>
                <li><strong>No single-item sections:</strong> Don't add a section with only 1 item.</li>
                <li><strong>Don't leave Single Select open</strong> after a choice is made.</li>
                <li><strong>Don't always show header</strong> even when it duplicates the trigger label.</li>
                <li><strong>Don't force manual reset:</strong> Don't make users uncheck each item to clear.</li>
              </ul></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <hr class="doc-divider"/>
          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="related" class="doc-section-title">Related</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Components that complement or can be used alongside the Dropdown Menu.</p>
            <div class="related-grid">
              <a href="#" class="related-chip"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h8"/></svg> Action Dropdown Item</a>
              <a href="Button.html" class="related-chip"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="14" rx="3"/></svg> Button</a>
              <a href="#" class="related-chip"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg> Select Field</a>
              <a href="#" class="related-chip"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="4"/><path d="M8 12h8"/></svg> Popover</a>
              <a href="Checkbox.html" class="related-chip"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg> Checkbox</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <hr class="doc-divider"/>
          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="references" class="doc-section-title">References</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Design tokens and resources for implementing the Dropdown Menu component.</p>
            <ul class="doc-list">
              <li><strong>Figma Node:</strong> <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">17286:257780</code> &#8212; Component Set: Dropdown Menu</li>
              <li><strong>Total Variants:</strong> 3 Types &times; 1 Size &times; 2 RTL = <strong>6 variants</strong></li>
              <li><strong>Typography:</strong> Zoho Puvi Regular (400) for items, Semi-bold (600) for headings/header</li>
              <li><strong>Border Radius:</strong> <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">8px</code> (panel and apply button)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ========== CODE ========== -->
        <div class="tab-content" id="tab-code" style="display:none;padding-top:32px;">
          <h2 id="live-demo-code" class="doc-section-title">Live demo (Code)</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Configure the Dropdown Menu component and view generated HTML.</p>
          <div class="code-playground">
            <div class="cp-toolbar">
              <div class="cp-control-group"><label class="cp-label">Type</label><select class="cp-select" id="pg-type"><option value="single">Single Select</option><option value="multi">Multi Select</option><option value="sections">With Sections</option></select></div>
              <div class="cp-control-group" id="pg-header-group"><label class="cp-label">Show Header</label><div class="cp-checkbox-wrap"><button class="cp-toggle on" id="pg-header-toggle"></button><span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);" id="pg-header-label">ON</span></div></div>
              <div class="cp-control-group" id="pg-footer-group"><label class="cp-label">Show Footer</label><div class="cp-checkbox-wrap"><button class="cp-toggle on" id="pg-footer-toggle"></button><span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);" id="pg-footer-label">ON</span></div></div>
              <div class="cp-control-group"><label class="cp-label">Direction</label><select class="cp-select" id="pg-dir"><option value="ltr">LTR</option><option value="rtl">RTL</option></select></div>
            </div>
            <div class="cp-preview" id="pg-preview-area"></div>
            <div class="cp-code-header">
              <div style="font-size:13.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);">HTML</div>
              <button class="cp-action-btn" id="pg-copy-btn"><svg width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7v8a2 2 0 002 2h6M8 7V5a2 2 0 012-2h4.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l4.414 4.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V15a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2M8 7H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2v-2"/></svg> Copy code</button>
            </div>
            <div class="cp-code-area" id="pg-code-output"></div>
          </div>
          <script>
          (function(){
            var typeEl = document.getElementById('pg-type');
            var headerToggle = document.getElementById('pg-header-toggle');
            var footerToggle = document.getElementById('pg-footer-toggle');
            var headerLabel = document.getElementById('pg-header-label');
            var footerLabel = document.getElementById('pg-footer-label');
            var headerGroup = document.getElementById('pg-header-group');
            var footerGroup = document.getElementById('pg-footer-group');
            var dirEl = document.getElementById('pg-dir');
            var previewArea = document.getElementById('pg-preview-area');
            var codeOut = document.getElementById('pg-code-output');
            var copyBtn = document.getElementById('pg-copy-btn');

            var showHeader = true, showFooter = true;

            headerToggle.addEventListener('click', function(){ showHeader = !showHeader; headerToggle.classList.toggle('on', showHeader); headerLabel.textContent = showHeader ? 'ON' : 'OFF'; update(); });
            footerToggle.addEventListener('click', function(){ showFooter = !showFooter; footerToggle.classList.toggle('on', showFooter); footerLabel.textContent = showFooter ? 'ON' : 'OFF'; update(); });

            function esc(s){return s.replace(/&/g,'&amp;').replace(/</g,'&lt;').replace(/>/g,'&gt;').replace(/"/g,'&quot;');}

            function update(){
              var type = typeEl.value;
              var dir = dirEl.value;
              var isMulti = type === 'multi';
              headerGroup.style.display = isMulti ? '' : 'none';
              footerGroup.style.display = isMulti ? '' : 'none';

              var html = '';
              var dirAttr = dir === 'rtl' ? ' dir="rtl"' : '';

              if (type === 'single') {
                html = '<div class="dd-panel"' + dirAttr + ' role="menu">\n';
                html += '  <div class="dd-item" role="menuitem">Edit</div>\n';
                html += '  <div class="dd-item" role="menuitem">Duplicate</div>\n';
                html += '  <div class="dd-item" role="menuitem">Share</div>\n';
                html += '  <div class="dd-item" role="menuitem">Delete</div>\n';
                html += '</div>';
              } else if (type === 'multi') {
                html = '<div class="dd-panel"' + dirAttr + ' role="menu">\n';
                if (showHeader) {
                  html += '  <div class="dd-header">\n';
                  html += '    <span>Select Options</span>\n';
                  html += '    <button aria-label="Dismiss">&times;</button>\n';
                  html += '  </div>\n';
                }
                html += '  <div class="dd-item" role="menuitemcheckbox" aria-checked="true">\n';
                html += '    <input type="checkbox" checked> Option A\n';
                html += '  </div>\n';
                html += '  <div class="dd-item" role="menuitemcheckbox" aria-checked="false">\n';
                html += '    <input type="checkbox"> Option B\n';
                html += '  </div>\n';
                html += '  <div class="dd-item" role="menuitemcheckbox" aria-checked="false">\n';
                html += '    <input type="checkbox"> Option C\n';
                html += '  </div>\n';
                if (showFooter) {
                  html += '  <div class="dd-footer">\n';
                  html += '    <button class="dd-clear-btn">Clear All</button>\n';
                  html += '    <button class="dd-apply-btn">Apply</button>\n';
                  html += '  </div>\n';
                }
                html += '</div>';
              } else {
                html = '<div class="dd-panel"' + dirAttr + ' role="menu">\n';
                html += '  <div class="dd-section-heading">Actions</div>\n';
                html += '  <div class="dd-item" role="menuitem">Edit</div>\n';
                html += '  <div class="dd-item" role="menuitem">Duplicate</div>\n';
                html += '  <div class="dd-divider" role="separator"></div>\n';
                html += '  <div class="dd-section-heading">More</div>\n';
                html += '  <div class="dd-item" role="menuitem">Share</div>\n';
                html += '  <div class="dd-item" role="menuitem">Archive</div>\n';
                html += '</div>';
              }

              // Build preview
              var previewHtml = '';
              if (type === 'single') {
                previewHtml = '<div class="dd-panel"' + (dir==='rtl'?' dir="rtl"':'') + '>';
                previewHtml += '<div class="dd-item"><svg class="dd-item-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#626870" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg><span>Edit</span></div>';
                previewHtml += '<div class="dd-item"><svg class="dd-item-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#626870" stroke-width="2"><path d="M16 4h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h2"/><rect x="8" y="2" width="8" height="4" rx="1"/></svg><span>Duplicate</span></div>';
                previewHtml += '<div class="dd-item"><svg class="dd-item-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#626870" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4 12v8a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2v-8"/><polyline points="16 6 12 2 8 6"/><line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="15"/></svg><span>Share</span></div>';
                previewHtml += '<div class="dd-item"><svg class="dd-item-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#626870" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="3 6 5 6 21 6"/><path d="M19 6v14a2 2 0 01-2 2H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V6m3 0V4a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v2"/></svg><span>Delete</span></div>';
                previewHtml += '</div>';
              } else if (type === 'multi') {
                previewHtml = '<div class="dd-panel"' + (dir==='rtl'?' dir="rtl"':'') + '>';
                if (showHeader) {
                  previewHtml += '<div class="dd-header"><span>Select Options</span><svg class="dd-header-dismiss" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#626870" stroke-width="2"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></div>';
                }
                previewHtml += '<div class="dd-item"><div class="dd-item-check checked"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div><span>Option A</span></div>';
                previewHtml += '<div class="dd-item"><div class="dd-item-check"></div><span>Option B</span></div>';
                previewHtml += '<div class="dd-item"><div class="dd-item-check"></div><span>Option C</span></div>';
                if (showFooter) {
                  previewHtml += '<div class="dd-footer"><button class="dd-clear-btn">Clear All</button><button class="dd-apply-btn">Apply</button></div>';
                }
                previewHtml += '</div>';
              } else {
                previewHtml = '<div class="dd-panel"' + (dir==='rtl'?' dir="rtl"':'') + '>';
                previewHtml += '<div class="dd-section-heading">Actions</div>';
                previewHtml += '<div class="dd-item"><svg class="dd-item-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#626870" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg><span>Edit</span></div>';
                previewHtml += '<div class="dd-item"><svg class="dd-item-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#626870" stroke-width="2"><path d="M16 4h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h2"/><rect x="8" y="2" width="8" height="4" rx="1"/></svg><span>Duplicate</span></div>';
                previewHtml += '<div class="dd-divider"></div>';
                previewHtml += '<div class="dd-section-heading">More</div>';
                previewHtml += '<div class="dd-item"><svg class="dd-item-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#626870" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4 12v8a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2v-8"/><polyline points="16 6 12 2 8 6"/><line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="15"/></svg><span>Share</span></div>';
                previewHtml += '<div class="dd-item"><svg class="dd-item-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#626870" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg><span>Archive</span></div>';
                previewHtml += '</div>';
              }
              previewArea.innerHTML = previewHtml;

              // Code output
              codeOut.innerHTML = esc(html)
                .replace(/class=&quot;(.*?)&quot;/g,'<span style="color:#38bdf8;">class</span>=<span style="color:#34d399;">"$1"</span>')
                .replace(/role=&quot;(.*?)&quot;/g,'<span style="color:#38bdf8;">role</span>=<span style="color:#34d399;">"$1"</span>')
                .replace(/aria-checked=&quot;(.*?)&quot;/g,'<span style="color:#38bdf8;">aria-checked</span>=<span style="color:#34d399;">"$1"</span>')
                .replace(/aria-label=&quot;(.*?)&quot;/g,'<span style="color:#38bdf8;">aria-label</span>=<span style="color:#34d399;">"$1"</span>')
                .replace(/dir=&quot;(.*?)&quot;/g,'<span style="color:#38bdf8;">dir</span>=<span style="color:#34d399;">"$1"</span>')
                .replace(/type=&quot;(.*?)&quot;/g,'<span style="color:#38bdf8;">type</span>=<span style="color:#34d399;">"$1"</span>')
                .replace(/ checked/g,' <span style="color:#38bdf8;">checked</span>')
                .replace(/&lt;(\/?)(div|button|input|span)(.*?)&gt;/g,'&lt;$1<span style="color:#a78bfa;">$2</span>$3&gt;');
            }

            typeEl.addEventListener('change', update);
            dirEl.addEventListener('change', update);
            copyBtn.addEventListener('click', function(){
              var r = document.createElement('div'); r.innerHTML = codeOut.innerHTML;
              navigator.clipboard.writeText(r.innerText).then(function(){
                var o = copyBtn.innerHTML; copyBtn.innerHTML='<svg width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Copied!'; setTimeout(function(){ copyBtn.innerHTML=o; },2000);
              });
            });
            update();
          })();
          </script>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>
          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="component-api-properties" class="doc-h3">Component API &amp; Properties</h3>
            <h4 style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:16px;">Panel Properties</h4>
            <table class="size-table" style="margin-bottom:32px;">
              <thead><tr><th>Property</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Applies To</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><code>Show Header</code></td><td>Boolean</td><td>ON</td><td>Multi Select</td><td>Toggles the header bar ("Select Options" + dismiss).</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Header Text</code></td><td>Text</td><td>"Select Options"</td><td>Multi Select</td><td>Editable title shown in the header.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Show Footer</code></td><td>Boolean</td><td>ON</td><td>Multi Select</td><td>Toggles the footer ("Clear All" + "Apply").</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
            <h4 style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:16px;">Action Dropdown Item Properties</h4>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Property</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><code>Label</code></td><td>Text</td><td>&#8212;</td><td>Item display text.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Type</code></td><td>Variant</td><td>Action item</td><td>Action item, Checkbox item, Section Heading, or Divider.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>State</code></td><td>Variant</td><td>Default</td><td>Default, Hover, Active, or Disabled.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Show Icon</code></td><td>Boolean</td><td>ON</td><td>Toggles the leading icon.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Leading Icon</code></td><td>Instance Swap</td><td>circle-plus</td><td>Swap the leading icon instance.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Selected</code></td><td>Boolean</td><td>OFF</td><td>Checkbox checked state (Multi Select only).</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <hr class="doc-divider"/>
          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="implementation-idea-ember-hook-form" class="doc-h3">Implementation Idea: Ember Hook Form</h3>
            <div class="cp-code-area" style="border-radius:12px;margin-top:16px;">
              <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.6;">
                <span style="color:#94a3b8;">&lt;!-- dropdown-menu.hbs --&gt;</span><br>
                <span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">UemsDropdownMenu</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">@type</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"multi"</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">@showHeader</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#C678DD;">{{</span><span style="color:#E5C07B;">true</span><span style="color:#C678DD;">}}</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">@headerText</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"Select Priority"</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">@showFooter</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#C678DD;">{{</span><span style="color:#E5C07B;">true</span><span style="color:#C678DD;">}}</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">@onApply</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#C678DD;">{{</span><span style="color:#E5C07B;">this.handleApply</span><span style="color:#C678DD;">}}</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">@onClear</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#C678DD;">{{</span><span style="color:#E5C07B;">this.handleClear</span><span style="color:#C678DD;">}}</span><br>
                <span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&nbsp;&nbsp;as |menu|</span><br>
                <span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">menu.Item</span>
                &nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">@label</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"High"</span>
                &nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">@selected</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#C678DD;">{{</span><span style="color:#E5C07B;">true</span><span style="color:#C678DD;">}}</span>
                <span style="color:#ABB2BF;"> /&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">menu.Item</span>
                &nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">@label</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"Medium"</span>
                <span style="color:#ABB2BF;"> /&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">menu.Item</span>
                &nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">@label</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"Low"</span>
                <span style="color:#ABB2BF;"> /&gt;</span><br>
                <span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;/</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">UemsDropdownMenu</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <hr class="doc-divider"/>
          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="rtl-support" class="doc-h3">RTL Support</h3>
            <ul class="doc-list">
              <li>When <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">RTL=True</code>, the entire panel is mirrored: header title moves right, dismiss icon moves left.</li>
              <li>Item icons appear on the <strong>right</strong> side, labels align <strong>right</strong>.</li>
              <li>Footer: "Apply" button moves to the <strong>left</strong>, "Clear All" to the <strong>right</strong>.</li>
              <li>Set <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">dir="rtl"</code> on the containing wrapper &#8212; do not mirror manually with CSS transforms.</li>
              <li>Use logical CSS properties (<code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">margin-inline-start</code>, <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">padding-inline-end</code>) for proper bidirectional support.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ========== ACCESSIBILITY ========== -->
        <div class="tab-content" id="tab-accessibility" style="display:none;padding-top:32px;">
          <h2 id="accessibility" class="doc-section-title">Accessibility</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Guidelines for ensuring dropdown menus are accessible across assistive technologies.</p>
          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="keyboard-interaction" class="doc-h3">Keyboard Interaction</h3>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Key</th><th>Action</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><code>&#8595; / &#8593;</code></td><td>Move focus between menu items.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Enter / Space</code></td><td>Activate the focused item or toggle a checkbox.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Escape</code></td><td>Close the menu and return focus to the trigger element.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Home</code></td><td>Move focus to the first menu item.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>End</code></td><td>Move focus to the last menu item.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Tab</code></td><td>Move focus to the next focusable element (footer buttons in Multi Select).</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
            <div style="margin-top:16px;padding:16px 20px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.15);border-radius:12px;">
              <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--prism-text);line-height:1.6;margin:0;">On open, focus moves to the first item in the list. On close (via Escape or selection in Single Select), focus returns to the trigger element that opened the menu.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <hr class="doc-divider"/>
          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="aria-attributes-screen-reader-guidance" class="doc-h3">ARIA Attributes &amp; Screen Reader Guidance</h3>
            <ul class="doc-list">
              <li><strong>role="menu"</strong> on the panel container to identify it as a menu to assistive technologies.</li>
              <li><strong>role="menuitem"</strong> for Single Select items; <strong>role="menuitemcheckbox"</strong> for Multi Select items.</li>
              <li><strong>aria-haspopup="menu"</strong> on the trigger element, combined with <strong>aria-expanded</strong> toggled on open/close.</li>
              <li><strong>aria-labelledby:</strong> Header text should be announced as the menu label via <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">aria-labelledby</code>.</li>
              <li><strong>Focus management:</strong> On open, focus moves to the first item. On close, focus returns to the trigger.</li>
              <li><strong>Multi Select Apply:</strong> The "Apply" button must be keyboard reachable and labeled <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">aria-label="Apply selection"</code> if icon-only.</li>
              <li><strong>RTL:</strong> Set <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">dir="rtl"</code> on the panel wrapper; rely on logical CSS properties.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <hr class="doc-divider"/>
          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="focus-state-design" class="doc-h3">Focus State Design</h3>
            <ul class="doc-list">
              <li>Focused menu items should display a visible focus ring (2px outline in the accent color, offset 2px).</li>
              <li>The focus indicator must be visible in both light and dark themes.</li>
              <li>Focus should not be trapped inside the menu &#8212; Tab key moves to footer buttons, then out of the panel.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <hr class="doc-divider"/>
          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="color-contrast-minimums" class="doc-h3">Color Contrast Minimums<span class="h3-badge" style="background:rgba(34,197,94,0.15);color:#16a34a;">WCAG AA Pass</span></h3>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">All text elements meet WCAG 2.1 AA contrast requirements against the white panel background.</p>
            <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:20px;margin-top:24px;">
              <div style="background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
                <div style="background:#FFFFFF;padding:28px 24px;text-align:center;color:#292A2E;border:1px solid #E0E3E8;border-radius:8px 8px 0 0;"><div style="font-size:24px;font-weight:600;">Edit</div></div>
                <div style="padding:16px 24px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;border-top:1px solid var(--prism-border);"><div><div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);font-weight:600;">ITEM TEXT</div><div style="font-size:15px;color:var(--prism-text);font-family:monospace;margin-top:4px;">#292A2E on #FFFFFF</div></div><div style="text-align:right;"><div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:rgba(34,197,94,0.1);color:#16a34a;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:100px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg> 15.4:1</div><div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:4px;font-weight:600;">WCAG AAA Pass</div></div></div>
              </div>
              <div style="background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
                <div style="background:#FFFFFF;padding:28px 24px;text-align:center;color:#626870;border:1px solid #E0E3E8;border-radius:8px 8px 0 0;"><div style="font-size:18px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.06em;">ACTIONS</div></div>
                <div style="padding:16px 24px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;border-top:1px solid var(--prism-border);"><div><div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);font-weight:600;">SECTION HEADING</div><div style="font-size:15px;color:var(--prism-text);font-family:monospace;margin-top:4px;">#626870 on #FFFFFF</div></div><div style="text-align:right;"><div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:rgba(34,197,94,0.1);color:#16a34a;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:100px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg> 5.5:1</div><div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:4px;font-weight:600;">WCAG AA Pass (3:1 min)</div></div></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <hr class="doc-divider"/>
          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="touch-target-size" class="doc-h3">Touch Target Size</h3>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Menu items must meet minimum touch target sizes on mobile devices.</p>
            <div style="margin-top:16px;padding:24px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:24px;">
              <div style="width:44px;height:44px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.1);border:1px dashed var(--prism-violet);border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--prism-violet);font-size:13px;font-weight:600;flex-shrink:0;">44px</div>
              <div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:var(--prism-text);">Menu Item: 44px minimum height on mobile</div><div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:4px;">Each menu item should have at least 44px of touch target height on mobile devices. On desktop, the smaller 32px height is acceptable since users have a mouse pointer.</div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        </div><!-- main-content-inner -->

        <aside class="toc-sidebar">
          <h4 class="toc-heading">On this page</h4>
